'''Yin-thi-ngî''' ([[Thiên-sàng-vùn]]: हिन्दी) yu chhṳ̂n-cho '''Pet Yin-thu-ngî''', he [[Yin-Êu Ngî-ne]] [[Yin-thu Yî-lóng Ngî-chhu̍k]] chûng [[Yin-thu Ngâ-li-ôn Ngî-kî]] hâ ke yit-chúng [[ngî-ngièn]]. 1965-ngièn 1-ngie̍t 26-ngit sṳ̀n-vì [[Yin-thu]] tûng-ông chṳn-fú ke [[kôn-fông ngî-ngièn]]. Yin-thi-ngî he sṳ-kie sông thi-ngi thai ngî-ngièn, mû- sṳ́-yung ngìn-khiéu chhêu-ko 180,000,000-ngìn. 1997-ngièn ke thiàu-chhà fat-hien 66% ke [[Yin-thu-ngìn]] hiáu-tet kóng [[Yin-thi-ngî]], 77% ke Yin-thu-ngìn chiông Yin-thi-ngî sṳ-vi koet-kâ ke khiung-thùng ngî-ngièn.

